title: #92Noon! Lavelle Neal/Gabe Henderson/Steve Hutchinson/Ron Johnson
description: Lavelle Neal opens the show with PA talking about the Twins recent losses to the Royals.  New Vikings Entertainment Network member Gabe Henderson talks to PA for the first time.  Former Viking and Hall of Famer Steve Hutchinson calls in to chat about his former team.  Plus, Ron Johnson joins for a jew segments to talk the Big 10 cancelling their season, and much more!
